Correct ways to run the script
oc rsh <kafka-broker-pod>
./clean.sh
 
 or 
 
 oc exec -it <kafka-broker-pod> -- ./clean.sh



Alternative: Deleting Kafka topics via Kafka CLI

to delete topic data, you can also use Kafka commands (inside the pod):

# Delete a topic
kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --delete --topic <topic-name>

# Delete all topics (careful!)
for topic in $(kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --list); do
  kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --delete --topic $topic
done


